body.description: Nourish your body with a reds and greens superfood supplement that's made from pure, organic fruits and vegetables with no fillers, preservatives, or additives. Most Americans struggle to meet the CDC’S recommended daily intake of fruits and veggies, and we can relate. After all, shopping for, storing, and preparing the fresh produce needed to consume the suggested 5-9 servings per day requires a lot of planning and work. Luckily, the Super Fruits and Super Veggies supplements we offer at Terra Kai Organics provide a quick and easy way to up your daily fruit and vegetable intake. Our fruit and veggies supplement contains a curated blend of 39 ultra nutritious plants that are packed with vitamins, minerals, and antioxidants. Most importantly, unlike synthetic vitamin pills, each serving contains whole food nutrients, fiber, and enzymes that work together to maximize absorption to provide real health benefits. We only use the highest quality plants to formulate our superfood supplements. Our Super Fruits and Super Veggies blends are made with non-GMO produce that's grown exclusively on organic farms, then harvested & freeze dried at peak ripeness to maximize nutrient retention. With a formula that's non-GMO, dairy free, gluten free, gelatin free, soy free & vegan, our fruit and vegetable capsules are an excellent source of supplemental nutrition for most diets. Show your body the love it deserves and try Super Fruits & Super Veggies today.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Organic Super Fruits & Veggies Whole food ingredients, powered by nutrient-rich plants in a convenient capsule. We harvest our ingredients from ORGANIC farmlands that use sustainable and regenerative methods that support bio-diversity and the environment. ORGANIC ensures our produce is free of pesticides and chemicals while sustainably grown produce preserves the integrity of our natural resources. Better for the Earth. Better for the future. • Organic Super Fruit & Veggie Nutrition • Antioxidants for Cellular Repair • Vegetable Fiber • Plant Based Energy • Mushrooms for Immune Support • NO Fillers • Simple and Convenient

Vegan Our Super Fruit & Veggie capsules are made of 100% vegan ingredients—even the capsules are gelatin free. We never add fillers or use preservatives —why would we when nature gave us these high quality ingredients? 100% Organic Our organic farming partners support sustainable farming practices that result in healthier soils and more nutrient rich produce. Better for you. Better for the earth. Better for the future. Non-GMO We’re obsessed with sourcing high quality, whole food ingredients. Ingredients that are 100% organic which means non-GMO too!

Supplement Facts Organic Super Fruits Organic Beet Root, Organic Raspberry, Organic Cranberry Juice, Organic Strawberry, Organic Carrot, Organic Blueberry Fruit, Organic Pomegranate Juice, Organic Acai Juice (Euterpe oleracea), Organic Blackberry, Organic Black Currant, Organic Cherry, Organic Acerola, Organic Bilberry Fruit, Organic Banana, Organic Apple, Organic Pineapple, Organic Orange Peel, Organic Mango, Organic Papaya, Organic Peach, Organic Pear, Organic Tomato, and Organic Lemon Peel. Organic Super Veggies Organic Spinach, Organic Spirulina, Organic Pea Fiber (hull), Organic Carrot, Organic Barley Grass, Organic Broccoli, Organic Kale, Organic Alfalfa (leaf), Organic Green Tea (shoots and leaf), and Organic Mushrooms (Organic Turkey Tail, Organic Lion’s Mane, Organic Chaga, Organic Maitake, Organic Reishi, Organic Shiitake, and Organic Agaricus blazei). Other Ingredients Hypromellose, Bamboo Stem and Leaf Extract, and L-leucine. Amount Per Serving 2000 milligrams Organic Super Fruits / 2000 milligrams Organic Super Veggies Directions Take 3 capsules each of Organic Super Fruits & Veggies daily for maximum benefits.

Our Story Growing up on my grandparent’s farm in the Pacific Northwest gave me an appreciation for fresh produce and small organic farms. Fresh fruits and vegetables were always on our table and lots of them! Our ingredients are harvested from organic farmlands and freeze-dried to preserve the highest nutritional value. I am proud to offer these easy-to-use super fruit and veggie capsules and grateful to our customers and the farmers who produce an abundance of the organic foods we eat.​ Super fruit and veggie capsules are our latest offering and great for a busy schedule and convenient for travel. Brought to you by the makers of JÚCE! —Adrian Vicente, Founder
